# Mojave v2 Field Guide — Five-Benchmark Measurement-Science Study

**Audience.** Mojave Claude, in-codebase coding agent, executing the v2 iteration of the public empirical study.
**Purpose.** Authoritative reference during eval setup, perturbation-matrix construction, run execution, variance decomposition, and publication. Consulted, not skimmed.
**Predecessor.** "Enter Mojave" (May 19 2026): 5 benchmarks × 106 perturbation variants × Qwen 2.5-7B-Instruct → 780 sealed run cards, 70–92 pp prompt-perturbation spread, prompt template + system prompt as dominant factors.
**Versioning convention.** If a tool is unpinned in this document, treat it as a TODO and verify the pin before run.

